title: News: Liberty League Test Case
subtitle: A New Deal agency is dragged into court.
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: event
view-if: spd_in_government = 1 and ((year = 1933 and month >= 3) or year > 1933) and news_cooldown_timer = 0 and supreme_court_hostility >= 3 and liberty_litigation >= 1
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: opposition_pressure += 1; supreme_court_hostility += 1; constitutional_stress += 1; news_cooldown_timer = 3
card-image: img/reichstag.jpg

= News: Liberty League Test Case

The Liberty League has found its case. A conservative district judge has accepted a challenge to one of the administration's recovery agencies, giving business papers a clean headline: **Can the New Deal govern by emergency?**

The legal question is narrow. The political question is not. Every hostile editorial treats the case as a referendum on whether the administration is rebuilding democracy or smuggling in permanent executive power.

- @lawyers: Fund a careful legal defense.
- @popular_case: Make the agency's beneficiaries visible.
- @quiet: Keep the fight quiet.

@lawyers
title: Fund a careful legal defense.
subtitle: -1 resources. Lowers court risk.
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: resources -= 1; supreme_court_hostility -= 1 if supreme_court_hostility > 0; liberty_litigation -= 1 if liberty_litigation > 0; agency_capacity += 1

The administration sends its best lawyers and avoids a grandstanding brief. The point is to win the case, not to give the Court a reason to strike broadly.

@popular_case
title: Make the agency's beneficiaries visible.
subtitle: Raises legitimacy, but politicizes the Court fight.
on-arrival: new_deal_legitimacy += 3 if new_deal_legitimacy < 95; workers_spd += 2; rural_spd += 2; supreme_court_hostility += 1; ddp_relation -= 2

Relief recipients, farmers, and local officials testify in public. The case becomes harder for opponents to describe as abstract constitutional housekeeping.

@quiet
title: Keep the fight quiet.
subtitle: Avoids escalation, but lets the opposition define the story.
on-arrival: liberty_litigation += 1; ddp_relation += 1; new_deal_legitimacy -= 1

The White House refuses to turn a court case into a national circus. The opposition has no such restraint.
